{
  "stem": "21139.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came here in August 1948, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] But before I came to London even, I was in Cheam in Surrey.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the last part of my training.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But that doesn't-- it's not so-- so important.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I-- August 10, 1948, I came to New York.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you speak any English?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I know you were in London for a while but--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I-- my English was quite good when I came to England, because I had private lessons in Germany, and I also had Spanish private lessons.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But English, I-- although I could not speak it, after a few months in England my ear got used to the sound, and I didn't have a problem.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, I went to first to school to finish high school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I-- it helped me when I was in training that I studied hard late at night, under the covers I used to study because the light had to be out at a certain time.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I-- I wanted to-- I didn't want to fail my exam.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I-- but English, it came fairly easy to me because I had a good foundation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came here by boat and the Nieuw-- with the and I arrived in-- I believe it was in Hoboken.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my cousin, my uncle, they were there to greet me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't speak to anyone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was shy, overwhelmed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know what the future will hold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was worried, although I had some family here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But still, I was, by that time, at an age where I have to, you know, I had to take care of myself.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't observe them, but I knew approximately when Yom Kippur, Rosh Hashanah should be.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
